data.description: Step into luxury with this exquisite 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom detached home, nestled on a corner lot within the much sought-after Grove at Vintage Oaks community. Spanning an impressive 3611 square feet, this 4 sided brick home offers both space and elegance.    The heart of the home features a cozy fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings. Work from home is a breeze in the dedicated office space, while the movie room promises endless entertainment for movie nights.    The community beckons with a lazy river, play ground, walking trails, and state-of-the-art fitness center, offering resort-style living at its best.    Don't miss the opportunity to own this spacious and serene haven. Set up a viewing and experience the perfect blend of luxury, community, and comfort today.
